OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMorning low cloud and fog will
OL,6,Fquickly disperse to leave a fine and
OL,7,Fsunny day. Any lingering fog offshore
OL,8,Fmay lap onto some coastal stretches at
OL,9,Ftimes. Feeling very warm in the July
OL,10,Fsunshine, with light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA warm and sunny evening.
OL,13,FStaying clear overnight, but the risk
OL,14,Fof some patches of mist and fog
OL,15,Fforming once more. A warm night for
OL,16,Fmost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
