OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FEarly fog clearing to leave a
OL,6,Fhot and sunny day across the region.
OL,7,FLight winds and high UV levels
OL,8,Fexpected. A very warm evening and
OL,9,Fnight to come too.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FPlenty
OL,12,Fof sunshine throughout. The wind
OL,13,Fpicking up a little may allow it to
OL,14,Ffeel not quite as hot for most.
OL,15,FPerhaps a few showers come Monday.
OL,16,FNights remaining warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
